WEBVTT

00:18.390 --> 00:20.590
I didn't expect this war to last so long.

00:20.800 --> 00:23.510
Does His Highness really plan
to enter peace talks?

00:23.510 --> 00:25.570
Will there really be peace from now on?

00:25.570 --> 00:26.870
Why aren't we fighting?

00:26.870 --> 00:28.280
The Monument of Loyalty was just erected.

00:28.280 --> 00:29.230
In the battle of Jiuzhang Plain,

00:29.230 --> 00:29.920
we clearly won.

00:29.920 --> 00:30.670
Runheng?

00:32.750 --> 00:33.280
Yuanji.

00:33.670 --> 00:34.530
Here they come.

00:37.110 --> 00:37.970
Here they come.

00:38.880 --> 00:39.680
They're here.

00:47.240 --> 00:48.170
Young Lord Xiao.

00:48.560 --> 00:49.710
I hope you have been well

00:48.960 --> 00:50.830
[Mu Lianyu, Eagle King]

00:50.030 --> 00:52.090
since our parting at Jiuzhang Plain.

00:52.840 --> 00:55.030
Eagle King, you have come a long way
for the peace talks.

00:55.030 --> 00:56.830
It must have been a hard journey.

00:57.560 --> 00:58.520
This is...

00:59.790 --> 01:01.600
This is the current Regent of Southern Ye,

01:01.600 --> 01:02.710
Prince Qi.

01:03.110 --> 01:03.920
Prince Qi?

01:04.760 --> 01:05.820
Never heard of him.

01:06.150 --> 01:08.920
Northern Qin cavalry
has fought Southern Ye for years.

01:08.920 --> 01:10.520
We only know Young Lord Xiao.

01:11.640 --> 01:12.270
It's fine.

01:12.890 --> 01:14.150
After the peace talks,

01:14.350 --> 01:16.120
you will naturally come to know me.

01:16.120 --> 01:16.640
Please.

01:16.920 --> 01:17.640
Hold on.

01:18.010 --> 01:20.830
Northern Qin and Southern Ye
have been at war for so many years.

01:20.830 --> 01:22.830
Since we are having peace talks now,

01:22.870 --> 01:24.310
we, Northern Qin, must also show

01:24.310 --> 01:25.640
our sincerity for them.

01:26.039 --> 01:27.840
I have specially prepared a gift

01:28.230 --> 01:29.230
for Southern Ye.

01:31.880 --> 01:34.600
23 years ago, we captured your Capital,

01:35.080 --> 01:38.440
forcing the Southern Ye royal family
to flee south to Jiankang.

01:38.440 --> 01:39.479
These are the royal descendants

01:39.479 --> 01:42.009
of Southern Ye
who couldn't escape back then.

01:42.039 --> 01:43.150
For all these years, Qin

01:43.150 --> 01:45.680
has been feeding
and providing for them well.

01:45.940 --> 01:47.440
Since we are having peace talks,

01:47.440 --> 01:48.640
we're sending them back

01:48.640 --> 01:50.039
to reunite their family.

01:50.070 --> 01:51.870
Wuyi, they are going too far.

01:53.110 --> 01:56.509
Northern Qin is also divided
into pro-war and pro-peace factions.

01:56.509 --> 01:59.509
The young Emperor wants peace,
but the Eagle King favors war.

01:59.509 --> 02:01.970
With the Eagle King
leading the delegation,

02:02.610 --> 02:04.400
the peace talks
will definitely not be easy.

02:04.400 --> 02:05.330
Young Lord Xiao.

02:07.590 --> 02:09.250
Your Highness, the Prince Qi.

02:09.310 --> 02:11.870
Can you see my sincerity?

02:14.070 --> 02:16.000
The Northern Qin people are going too far!

02:16.000 --> 02:16.800
Stop them!

02:17.079 --> 02:18.240
Stop them! Hurry, stop them!

02:18.240 --> 02:19.680
Stop them!

02:20.470 --> 02:21.400
This is too much!

02:21.520 --> 02:22.840
Humiliating our people!

02:22.840 --> 02:23.630
Stop them!

02:24.120 --> 02:24.710
Yuanji.

02:26.840 --> 02:27.570
You animals!

02:27.840 --> 02:28.520
Eagle King.

02:31.370 --> 02:32.120
Please.

02:32.390 --> 02:33.190
Stop them!

03:59.270 --> 04:03.270
[Key to the Phoenix Heart]

04:03.620 --> 04:06.170
[Episode 8]

04:06.240 --> 04:07.590
The Northern Qin barbarians

04:06.310 --> 04:08.530
[Honglu Temple]

04:07.590 --> 04:08.960
humiliated our nation.

04:09.000 --> 04:10.400
No peace talks!

04:10.590 --> 04:12.080
The Northern Qin barbarians

04:12.080 --> 04:13.410
humiliated our nation.

04:13.630 --> 04:15.080
No peace talks!

04:17.510 --> 04:18.140
Come on.

04:18.510 --> 04:19.190
Let's go.

04:23.920 --> 04:24.600
My Lady.

04:25.360 --> 04:26.630
This is Honglu Temple.

04:26.950 --> 04:28.480
We should probably go back.

04:29.160 --> 04:30.830
The Eagle King
humiliated our royal family.

04:30.830 --> 04:32.110
This is outrageous!

04:32.240 --> 04:33.560
Didn't you hear what Yan Yue just said?

04:33.560 --> 04:34.870
The students are filled
with righteous indignation

04:34.870 --> 04:36.450
and have completely surrounded
the Honglu Temple,

04:36.450 --> 04:38.000
just waiting to charge in
and hack down the Eagle King.

04:38.000 --> 04:39.130
Even Mao went there.

04:40.250 --> 04:41.210
But Xiao Wuyi

04:41.600 --> 04:43.190
keeps the Beifu soldiers
confined to the camp,

04:43.190 --> 04:44.850
not letting any news leak out.

04:44.870 --> 04:46.880
What "bloodthirsty Yama Xiao"
are they talking about?

04:46.880 --> 04:47.990
If something really happens,

04:47.990 --> 04:49.650
he'd only act tough around us.

04:49.920 --> 04:51.720
So we must hurry in and help Mao.

04:52.040 --> 04:54.500
We can't let him
be bullied by the Eagle King.

04:58.600 --> 04:59.310
This...

05:00.430 --> 05:02.160
What's wrong with your throat?

05:07.880 --> 05:09.420
You secretly take the fire thunderstone.

05:09.420 --> 05:12.720
Do you want to go to the Honglu Temple
and blow up the Eagle King?

05:12.720 --> 05:13.390
No, no.

05:14.120 --> 05:15.050
I really didn't.

05:15.950 --> 05:17.430
Stop. I'll tell you.

05:18.040 --> 05:20.630
I heard that the Eagle King
coming for the peace talks

05:20.630 --> 05:21.870
has a Longque Blade.

05:22.160 --> 05:23.600
I want to see it.

05:23.950 --> 05:24.800
I also want to see

05:24.800 --> 05:26.240
how the legendary number
one blade in the world

05:26.240 --> 05:27.360
is forged.

05:27.360 --> 05:28.480
Know yourself and your enemy, right?

05:28.480 --> 05:29.920
If only I could also forge

05:30.310 --> 05:32.640
such a world-renowned, peerless weapon.

05:33.750 --> 05:35.830
Do I look stupid and easy to fool?

05:36.950 --> 05:37.750
Really.

05:38.120 --> 05:39.360
If I can actually forge it,

05:39.360 --> 05:40.000
I'll give the first one to you.

05:40.000 --> 05:42.000
The peace talks concern
the lifeblood of Ye.

05:42.000 --> 05:43.430
If you dare to mess around...

05:43.430 --> 05:44.630
Forget it if you don't believe me.

05:44.630 --> 05:45.510
So naggy.

05:45.560 --> 05:47.070
You might as well tie me to your belt.

05:47.070 --> 05:47.510
Okay.

05:58.159 --> 05:59.190
Why did you skip the front door

05:59.190 --> 05:59.830
and fly up here?

05:59.830 --> 06:01.600
If you're worried, go see for yourself.

06:01.600 --> 06:03.120
The Northern Qin barbarians

06:03.120 --> 06:04.450
humiliated our nation.

06:04.510 --> 06:06.000
No peace talks!

06:06.120 --> 06:07.360
They humiliated our nation.

06:07.360 --> 06:08.680
No peace talks!

06:09.390 --> 06:10.720
They humiliated our nation.

06:10.720 --> 06:11.720
No peace talks!

06:12.120 --> 06:13.510
This is Ye's territory.

06:13.830 --> 06:15.750
Northern Qin lost the war.

06:15.750 --> 06:17.560
They're the ones suing for peace now.

06:17.560 --> 06:20.820
I don't believe he dares
to kill people in the capital of Ye!

06:20.920 --> 06:21.560
Move away!

06:21.760 --> 06:22.410
Move away!

06:25.070 --> 06:25.720
Yizhi.

06:28.360 --> 06:29.230
Your Highness Prince Qi.

06:29.230 --> 06:30.330
You're finally here.

06:30.330 --> 06:32.490
Northern Qin humiliated our royal family.

06:32.490 --> 06:34.000
We were extremely angry upon hearing this.

06:34.000 --> 06:36.260
If this can be tolerated, what cannot be?

06:36.310 --> 06:39.070
If the Eagle King doesn't
remove his crown and beg for forgiveness,

06:39.070 --> 06:40.920
we will never agree to these peace talks!

06:40.920 --> 06:44.159
We'll never agree!

06:44.159 --> 06:45.480
What is this commotion?

06:45.480 --> 06:48.140
Have you forgotten
what your master taught you?

06:48.190 --> 06:50.040
Students should
concentrate on their studies

06:50.040 --> 06:51.630
and not discuss state affairs.

06:51.630 --> 06:52.870
Regarding this matter,

06:52.870 --> 06:55.360
I will discuss with Young Lord Xiao
to find a resolution.

06:55.360 --> 06:56.270
You all leave first.

06:56.270 --> 06:57.000
Your Highness.

06:57.000 --> 06:58.870
Even the current regent
hosting the peace talks

06:58.870 --> 07:00.130
is acting so cowardly.

07:00.310 --> 07:01.430
Those Northern Qin bastards

07:01.430 --> 07:02.600
have already walked all over us,

07:02.600 --> 07:03.800
yet you still endure blindly.

07:03.800 --> 07:05.630
Scholars neglect statecraft;
warriors neglect warfare.

07:05.630 --> 07:06.750
Ye is doomed.

07:07.120 --> 07:07.920
Nonsense!

07:08.110 --> 07:08.950
Throw!

07:10.630 --> 07:13.070
No peace talks!

07:27.480 --> 07:29.340
You said you came to see the blade.

07:29.840 --> 07:31.720
But we can't just stand here and watch.

07:31.720 --> 07:33.190
Are you this cowardly
on the battlefield, too?

07:33.190 --> 07:34.120
How did you win your battles?

07:34.120 --> 07:37.270
Do you think fighting a war is
just hacking at each other with blades?

07:37.270 --> 07:39.090
Let me tell you the first rule
of the art of war.

07:39.090 --> 07:41.040
War is a matter
of vital importance to the state.

07:41.040 --> 07:43.070
It is a matter of life and death,
a road either to safety or to ruin.

07:43.070 --> 07:44.800
It must be thoroughly studied.

07:47.680 --> 07:48.360
Stop!

07:48.450 --> 07:49.650
Move away! Move away!

07:56.240 --> 07:57.370
Young Lord Xiao said

07:57.680 --> 07:59.120
that peace talks are state policy

07:59.120 --> 07:59.920
and cannot be changed.

07:59.920 --> 08:01.680
Considering that you are
young and hot-blooded,

08:01.680 --> 08:03.280
and the future pillars of Ye,

08:03.310 --> 08:04.830
you will be lightly punished today
as a warning—

08:04.830 --> 08:06.090
20 strokes of the cane.

08:06.430 --> 08:07.360
General Yan Yue,

08:07.600 --> 08:08.830
this is inappropriate.

08:08.830 --> 08:10.720
The students are acting out of patriotism.

08:10.720 --> 08:12.870
It is exactly because His Highness
considers their patriotism

08:12.870 --> 08:14.270
that they are only getting 20 strokes.

08:14.270 --> 08:15.400
Under military law,

08:15.800 --> 08:17.950
those who violate orders die.

08:18.560 --> 08:19.870
Anyone else who misleads the public

08:19.870 --> 08:21.310
and disrupts the peace talks

08:21.310 --> 08:22.600
will be executed without fail.

08:22.600 --> 08:23.190
Hit!

08:24.040 --> 08:25.190
What are you doing?

08:25.190 --> 08:25.950
How can you hit people?

08:25.950 --> 08:27.680
Let go of me! What are you doing?

08:28.600 --> 08:29.660
Xiao Wuyi, this...

08:29.950 --> 08:32.030
Xiao Wuyi, how dare you hit me?

08:33.240 --> 08:35.030
Yizhi, save me!

08:35.030 --> 08:36.440
He even dares to kill officials.

08:36.440 --> 08:38.080
The Empress Dowager
can't even deal with him.

08:38.080 --> 08:39.320
Why wouldn't he?

08:39.750 --> 08:40.610
Your Highness,

08:41.270 --> 08:42.549
His Highness asks you
to return to the Eastern Palace

08:42.549 --> 08:44.390
to continue drafting the peace treaty.

08:44.390 --> 08:45.850
Leave matters here to him.

08:47.000 --> 08:47.550
Please.

08:53.510 --> 08:54.910
Execute the punishment one by one.

08:54.910 --> 08:55.510
Look,

08:56.270 --> 08:57.270
isn't it solved?

08:58.430 --> 08:58.860
Hey.

08:59.750 --> 09:01.390
Is this the solution you figured out?

09:01.390 --> 09:02.980
Those are Mao's classmates and friends,

09:02.980 --> 09:04.580
and you just had them beaten?

09:04.750 --> 09:07.410
Xiao Wuyi, are you
that afraid of the Eagle King?

09:07.440 --> 09:08.800
I really misjudged you.

09:12.870 --> 09:16.200
Young Lord Xiao, His Highness,
the Eagle King, invites you.

09:19.270 --> 09:19.870
Xiao Wuyi!

09:19.910 --> 09:21.360
H-How do I get down?

09:22.270 --> 09:24.630
If you still want to play
with fire in the future,

09:24.630 --> 09:26.120
you must first learn how to run away.

09:26.120 --> 09:27.120
What about today?

09:27.750 --> 09:29.080
Figure it out yourself.

09:29.840 --> 09:30.440
Figure...

09:31.670 --> 09:32.360
You...

09:32.470 --> 09:32.840
I—

09:33.960 --> 09:34.440
I...

09:34.790 --> 09:35.360
I...

09:40.120 --> 09:41.360
Speaking of mutton,

09:42.080 --> 09:44.480
it's still the best
on Northern Qin grasslands.

09:44.480 --> 09:45.910
It doesn't have any gamey smell.

09:45.910 --> 09:47.170
Your Highness, try it.

09:50.200 --> 09:51.010
Mu Lianyu,

09:51.820 --> 09:53.680
you don't want peace talks at all.

09:56.000 --> 09:58.000
Your Highness tramples
on the people's will like this.

09:58.000 --> 10:00.750
Aren't you afraid that the commoners
will hate the Beifu Army

10:00.750 --> 10:01.600
and you?

10:02.000 --> 10:03.660
The people's will can be used,

10:03.670 --> 10:05.240
but cannot be fully trusted.

10:05.240 --> 10:08.400
You went to great lengths
to provoke today's public anger.

10:08.400 --> 10:10.100
You just hope that Ye will call off

10:10.100 --> 10:11.360
the peace talks first,

10:11.440 --> 10:13.640
so you can answer to your little emperor

10:13.840 --> 10:15.300
without taking the blame.

10:17.750 --> 10:19.390
I really didn't expect

10:19.630 --> 10:22.030
that the decisive
Young Lord Xiao on the battlefield

10:22.030 --> 10:24.870
would be so forbearing
off the battlefield.

10:25.390 --> 10:28.510
It seems you're having
a hard time in Jiankang.

10:29.440 --> 10:30.700
The feeling is mutual.

10:32.670 --> 10:34.240
If it weren't for the heavy snow,

10:34.240 --> 10:35.440
we wouldn't have lost

10:35.510 --> 10:37.170
the battle at Jiuzhang Plain.

10:37.270 --> 10:38.360
In terms of archery and horsemanship,

10:38.360 --> 10:40.550
our Northern Qin is far superior
to your Southern Ye.

10:40.550 --> 10:41.790
But you lost.

10:43.630 --> 10:45.030
Otherwise, I wouldn't be able
to eat

10:45.030 --> 10:46.950
Northern Qin's roasted mutton in Jiankang.

10:46.950 --> 10:47.550
Mu Lianyu.

10:48.000 --> 10:50.120
Now your little emperor
also wants peace talks.

10:50.120 --> 10:51.920
That's why you are sitting here.

10:52.320 --> 10:53.510
Please stop your tricks.

10:53.510 --> 10:54.710
Don't try to anger me.

10:57.240 --> 10:58.200
I can bear

10:59.110 --> 11:00.240
the people's anger.

11:08.510 --> 11:10.720
Today, I have finally seen

11:11.360 --> 11:13.360
your sincerity in the peace talks.

11:13.840 --> 11:15.440
The most difficult part of the peace talks

11:15.440 --> 11:18.040
is the ownership
of the three northern prefectures.

11:18.040 --> 11:19.040
In that case,

11:19.830 --> 11:21.920
why don't our countries

11:22.320 --> 11:24.750
compete in public to determine

11:24.990 --> 11:25.990
their ownership?

11:28.150 --> 11:31.210
I wonder if Southern Ye
dares to accept this challenge.

11:32.030 --> 11:33.030
How do we compete?

11:33.320 --> 11:35.780
Very simple.
Shoot the willow on horseback—

11:36.240 --> 11:37.570
a game of life and death.

11:38.360 --> 11:39.560
Do you dare to accept?

11:46.240 --> 11:47.970
Shoot the willow on horseback.

11:48.960 --> 11:50.960
Each country will send three people
and three horses,

11:50.960 --> 11:52.200
with three arrows per person.

11:52.200 --> 11:53.600
When all arrows are shot,

11:53.730 --> 11:56.150
whichever country
has more arrows left on the target

11:56.150 --> 11:58.280
gets the three northern prefectures.

11:59.320 --> 12:01.240
Your Majesty, the Empress Dowager,
these three prefectures

12:01.240 --> 12:02.790
were originally the territory of Ye.

12:02.790 --> 12:05.320
It's the Qin people
who have been invading us.

12:05.390 --> 12:07.150
How can we use such a child's play

12:07.150 --> 12:09.680
to determine the ownership
of our territory?

12:10.000 --> 12:12.360
Young Lord Xiao, what do you think?

12:18.000 --> 12:19.550
He proposed this competition

12:19.550 --> 12:20.870
simply because he doesn't
want peace talks

12:20.870 --> 12:22.600
and wants to force us to refuse.

12:22.670 --> 12:23.720
Even if we agree,

12:24.240 --> 12:26.960
he just wants to use this competition
to win back their pride.

12:26.960 --> 12:27.840
In that case,

12:28.670 --> 12:29.960
we shall fight again

12:30.630 --> 12:32.470
and make him admit defeat.

12:34.960 --> 12:36.670
Can you guarantee a sure win,
Your Highness?

12:36.670 --> 12:38.200
Matters on the battlefield

12:38.320 --> 12:39.720
can never be guaranteed.

12:41.910 --> 12:43.510
Even you can't guarantee it.

12:44.080 --> 12:45.240
If we win this battle,

12:45.240 --> 12:46.990
we might finally hold our heads high.

12:46.990 --> 12:48.050
But what if we lose?

12:48.240 --> 12:50.320
Your Highness and the Beifu Army
will be ruined.

12:50.320 --> 12:52.480
The three northern prefectures
will fall into the hands of the Qin.

12:52.480 --> 12:53.870
The advantage of our
peace talks with Northern Qin

12:53.870 --> 12:55.080
will also be gone.

12:55.080 --> 12:56.380
Have you considered this, Young Lord Xiao?

12:56.380 --> 12:58.180
If every battle were a sure win,

12:58.570 --> 13:00.500
there would be no war in this world.

13:03.370 --> 13:04.290
Let us fight.

13:05.390 --> 13:06.150
Let the people and scholars

13:06.150 --> 13:08.000
who are criticizing me see

13:08.320 --> 13:09.600
that the peace talks I led

13:09.600 --> 13:11.120
were for the future of Ye,

13:12.240 --> 13:13.640
not because I feared war.

13:21.240 --> 13:24.240
I am willing to fight Northern Qin!

13:30.960 --> 13:31.560
Wuyi.

13:33.480 --> 13:34.120
Wuyi.

13:35.010 --> 13:36.200
Northern Qin
was founded on military might.

13:36.200 --> 13:37.240
Their people excel
in archery and horsemanship.

13:37.240 --> 13:38.150
Are you really confident?

13:38.150 --> 13:39.910
Yizhi, why not think
about it the other way around?

13:39.910 --> 13:41.750
If Northern Qin
loses even the horse archery

13:41.750 --> 13:42.910
they are most proud of to us,

13:42.910 --> 13:44.840
and loses three prefectures
because of it,

13:44.840 --> 13:46.050
what will happen within Northern Qin?

13:46.050 --> 13:47.080
Their morale will plummet.

13:47.080 --> 13:48.630
But that's easier said than done.

13:48.630 --> 13:49.510
In this archery competition,

13:49.510 --> 13:50.630
arrows can not only shoot targets,

13:50.630 --> 13:51.960
but also people and horses.

13:51.960 --> 13:52.720
In the arena,

13:53.270 --> 13:54.630
the Eagle King will definitely
use lethal moves against you.

13:54.630 --> 13:55.600
Then let's see if he has

13:55.600 --> 13:57.200
what it takes to take my life.

14:01.200 --> 14:01.790
Yizhi.

14:06.360 --> 14:08.020
I'm sorry about what happened

14:09.820 --> 14:11.620
at the Honglu Temple yesterday.

14:12.320 --> 14:13.440
I had no choice.

14:15.030 --> 14:16.560
You don't need to say this to me.

14:16.560 --> 14:17.820
I believe in you, Wuyi.

14:19.080 --> 14:21.150
But for the peace talks,

14:21.440 --> 14:22.840
what is your bottom line?

14:24.390 --> 14:25.120
Time.

14:25.870 --> 14:26.510
Time?

14:26.630 --> 14:28.030
Conditions are not important,

14:28.030 --> 14:30.480
but the reform of the Beifu
needs at least three years of peace.

14:30.480 --> 14:32.030
I am confident that after the reform,

14:32.030 --> 14:33.720
I can increase
the Beifu Army's combat power by 80%.

14:33.720 --> 14:34.720
As long as I have time,

14:34.720 --> 14:37.030
the Northern Expedition
will definitely succeed.

14:37.030 --> 14:38.490
So no matter what happens,

14:38.630 --> 14:40.000
no matter what tricks the Eagle King

14:40.000 --> 14:40.870
has waiting for me,

14:40.870 --> 14:42.930
I must make the peace talks a success.

14:43.360 --> 14:44.000
Wuyi,

14:44.510 --> 14:46.910
I really envy
your boldness and determination.

14:46.910 --> 14:47.960
Ye can lose three prefectures,

14:47.960 --> 14:50.150
but we absolutely cannot lose you,
Xiao Wuyi.

14:50.150 --> 14:51.600
Losing three prefectures
is a temporary loss.

14:51.600 --> 14:54.260
Losing Wuyi means
losing the nation's destiny.

14:54.480 --> 14:55.270
In the arena,

14:55.550 --> 14:56.550
you must be very careful.

14:56.550 --> 14:57.480
Li Yizhi,

14:58.050 --> 14:59.890
since when did you become
so good at flattering?

14:59.890 --> 15:02.150
I'm speaking from the bottom of my heart.

15:02.240 --> 15:04.000
You don't know how much I envy you

15:04.000 --> 15:06.530
for building your career
with your own hands.

15:11.080 --> 15:11.750
Wuyi.

15:13.390 --> 15:14.590
Do you want me to stay?

15:20.150 --> 15:21.480
Do you think I, Li Yizhi,

15:22.200 --> 15:24.460
am worthy of being the Crown Prince of Ye?

15:32.000 --> 15:33.120
I didn't expect you, Xiao Wuyi,

15:33.120 --> 15:34.120
to be speechless.

15:34.600 --> 15:36.260
Never mind. I was just asking.

15:36.290 --> 15:37.600
Don't take it seriously.

15:37.600 --> 15:38.910
Jiayu doesn't like the palace.

15:38.910 --> 15:39.720
Even for her sake,

15:39.720 --> 15:40.630
I can't stay.

15:41.130 --> 15:41.730
By the way,

15:42.200 --> 15:43.360
the hawthorn cakes she made last time

15:43.360 --> 15:44.490
tasted really good.

15:44.630 --> 15:45.790
I am not used to the food in the palace.

15:45.790 --> 15:47.240
I rely entirely on them
to whet my appetite.

15:47.240 --> 15:48.390
Could I trouble you

15:49.120 --> 15:50.980
to ask her to make some more for me?

15:52.120 --> 15:52.750
I got it.

16:05.600 --> 16:07.670
Later, let's give all the medicinal herbs

16:07.670 --> 16:09.070
we brought today to them.

16:10.960 --> 16:12.620
I'll go take a look over there.

16:18.630 --> 16:23.810
Master. Master. Master.

16:23.840 --> 16:25.960
I told you to study behind closed doors

16:25.960 --> 16:27.670
and not discuss state affairs.

16:27.670 --> 16:28.580
What about you?

16:28.850 --> 16:30.850
Did you even listen to me?

16:32.150 --> 16:34.280
Do not get involved in the peace talks.

16:35.150 --> 16:36.670
I am getting old

16:37.200 --> 16:39.660
and don't have many days
left to protect you.

16:39.990 --> 16:41.160
Please don't

16:41.200 --> 16:43.550
cause any more trouble blindly,

16:43.550 --> 16:44.440
okay?

16:44.630 --> 16:45.320
Master.

16:46.670 --> 16:48.670
It's not that we are acting blindly.

16:49.030 --> 16:51.360
The Northern Qin people
have gone too far.

16:51.720 --> 16:53.030
We study the books of the sages.

16:53.030 --> 16:54.240
How could we just sit by and watch?

16:54.240 --> 16:55.040
Today's blood

16:55.320 --> 16:56.510
is not to cause trouble,

16:56.510 --> 16:57.600
but to wake the people.

16:57.600 --> 16:58.750
And Xiao Wuyi,

16:59.360 --> 17:00.720
as the commander of the Beifu Army,

17:00.720 --> 17:01.480
to fear the enemy

17:01.480 --> 17:03.030
and abandon the people like this
just for peace talks

17:03.030 --> 17:04.400
is an absolute disgrace!

17:04.400 --> 17:05.240
Exactly.

17:05.960 --> 17:06.680
Enough.

17:12.829 --> 17:14.960
Has your mother sent you any messages?

17:17.210 --> 17:19.170
Shouldn't she be at home?

17:21.960 --> 17:22.750
Yaoyao,

17:24.349 --> 17:26.790
I am your father.

17:29.070 --> 17:31.200
You've never been good at lying.

17:32.200 --> 17:33.680
Your mother divorced me.

17:33.960 --> 17:35.620
She wouldn't keep it from you.

17:38.030 --> 17:39.350
She did leave a letter.

17:40.030 --> 17:41.030
She said all these years,

17:41.030 --> 17:43.510
trapped in Jiankang Palace
and the Grand Tutor's Mansion,

17:43.510 --> 17:44.710
she was very unhappy.

17:44.830 --> 17:46.030
Now that I'm married,

17:46.830 --> 17:48.630
she can finally follow her heart

17:48.960 --> 17:50.490
and live the life she wants.

17:51.240 --> 17:52.200
She also said

17:52.480 --> 17:54.200
the divorce is between you two.

17:54.200 --> 17:55.460
She is still my mother,

17:58.420 --> 17:59.950
and you are still my father.

18:00.790 --> 18:02.030
That's all she said.

18:02.880 --> 18:04.480
Even if I knew where she went,

18:04.750 --> 18:05.880
I wouldn't tell you.

18:09.150 --> 18:10.550
If there's nothing else,

18:11.070 --> 18:12.070
I will leave now.

18:14.400 --> 18:15.960
For this round of peace talks,

18:15.960 --> 18:17.820
a Northern Qin official proposed

18:18.270 --> 18:21.030
to send a royal daughter
to marry into Northern Qin.

18:21.030 --> 18:22.590
Who do you think

18:22.920 --> 18:25.790
is the most suitable
among the Jiankang royals now?

18:28.440 --> 18:29.240
Li Lejun.

18:31.110 --> 18:32.550
You want to send Lejun away
for a political marriage?

18:32.550 --> 18:33.750
It's not us.

18:35.640 --> 18:37.070
It's Xiao Wuyi.

18:37.750 --> 18:39.070
Looking at his current actions,

18:39.070 --> 18:41.960
you can tell he will definitely
make sure the peace talks succeed,

18:41.960 --> 18:43.550
no matter what it takes.

18:45.750 --> 18:47.030
Everyone knows
the miserable and maddened state

18:47.030 --> 18:48.270
of the Southern Ye royal clan

18:48.270 --> 18:51.200
inside the iron cage outside
the city gates that day.

18:51.350 --> 18:55.280
You surely wouldn't want Princess Pingning
to suffer such a disaster,

18:55.400 --> 18:56.000
right?

18:57.510 --> 18:59.270
If you want to protect her...

19:02.920 --> 19:04.160
I

19:06.070 --> 19:07.510
can help.

19:09.580 --> 19:10.580
What's the price?

19:11.250 --> 19:11.810
Father,

19:13.290 --> 19:15.020
what do you want me to do for you?

19:15.200 --> 19:17.720
The peace talks may succeed,

19:18.490 --> 19:19.640
but Xiao Wuyi

19:22.380 --> 19:23.200
must lose.

19:28.890 --> 19:29.480
Lose?

19:32.790 --> 19:34.920
Coincidentally, the bone is injured.

19:35.440 --> 19:38.100
You must give him
the medicine on time, as I said.

19:44.480 --> 19:45.310
Pei Runheng?

19:46.510 --> 19:48.070
Wake up.

19:48.750 --> 19:49.400
Doctor.

19:50.550 --> 19:51.410
Your Highness.

19:51.550 --> 19:52.440
Do you know him?

19:53.510 --> 19:55.070
He is badly injured.

19:55.550 --> 19:56.920
Doctor, come here.

19:58.960 --> 20:00.400
Wake up. Wake up.

20:11.440 --> 20:13.700
The noble clans are committing treason.

20:14.160 --> 20:15.960
They are parasites of the state.

20:18.270 --> 20:18.920
Runheng.

20:19.160 --> 20:20.420
-Who is Runheng?
-You—

20:21.400 --> 20:22.000
Go away.

20:23.000 --> 20:23.860
Don't touch me.

20:31.110 --> 20:33.680
Do you know that scholar?

20:36.920 --> 20:38.650
I mistook him for someone else.

20:38.920 --> 20:42.110
He looks a lot like an old friend of mine.

20:42.920 --> 20:45.270
Runheng would never look at me

20:45.750 --> 20:47.880
with such unfamiliarity and disgust.

20:47.960 --> 20:48.550
Besides,

20:49.160 --> 20:50.720
I saw Runheng's body.

20:51.240 --> 20:54.550
Mr. Runheng was your sweetheart?

20:58.310 --> 20:59.920
On the day of the Double Ninth Ceremony,

20:59.920 --> 21:01.030
I saw the prayer tablet you wrote

21:01.030 --> 21:02.480
on the prayer tree.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.240
That name was on it.

21:05.000 --> 21:07.860
But I didn't expect
that he had already passed away.

21:07.920 --> 21:09.640
The prayer tree
on the Double Ninth Festival

21:09.640 --> 21:11.400
is also called the Yin-Yang Tree.

21:11.400 --> 21:14.400
It was originally meant to commemorate
friendship with the deceased.

21:14.400 --> 21:15.110
What?

21:15.920 --> 21:17.180
Then Ruisheng also...

21:20.110 --> 21:23.030
So you married Xiao Wuyi

21:23.270 --> 21:25.200
because your sweetheart was gone?

21:27.030 --> 21:28.880
It was because
I was going to marry Xiao Wuyi

21:28.880 --> 21:29.960
I beg Your Majesty, Empress Dowager
for mercy,

21:29.960 --> 21:30.960
that he was gone.

21:30.960 --> 21:32.160
I'm already engaged.

21:37.200 --> 21:38.830
His Majesty has just ascended the throne,

21:38.830 --> 21:40.310
and his position is still unstable.

21:40.310 --> 21:42.370
And the Beifu Army needs provisions.

21:43.030 --> 21:45.550
Now is a good time
for the He family and the Xiao family

21:45.550 --> 21:47.150
to form a marriage alliance.

21:48.110 --> 21:50.570
If you weren't the only eligible
in the clan,

21:50.790 --> 21:52.120
I would never force you.

21:53.350 --> 21:53.960
Aunt.

21:55.070 --> 21:55.830
Aunt.

21:59.250 --> 22:01.510
And I made the most regrettable decision

22:01.640 --> 22:02.750
in my life.

22:04.240 --> 22:05.110
What was it?

22:08.270 --> 22:10.110
I told my parents and the Empress Dowager

22:10.110 --> 22:11.880
that I already had a sweetheart,

22:11.880 --> 22:13.740
letting them know about Runheng.

22:14.310 --> 22:16.640
Runheng was the son
of the academy's headmaster

22:16.640 --> 22:19.170
and a distant relative
of my mother's family.

22:19.270 --> 22:21.200
I thought my parents would help me.

22:21.590 --> 22:22.720
But not long after,

22:23.160 --> 22:24.070
what I received

22:25.550 --> 22:27.480
was actually the news of his death.

22:28.960 --> 22:30.310
Later, I found out

22:30.310 --> 22:32.750
that the border military situation
was urgent at that time,

22:32.750 --> 22:35.200
and the Beifu Army urgently needed
the He family's provision of support.

22:35.200 --> 22:37.550
Because I kept refusing
to agree to the marriage,

22:37.550 --> 22:39.720
the forces of the Empress Dowager
and the Heir

22:39.720 --> 22:41.320
had both gone to look for him.

22:41.370 --> 22:44.760
So someone murdered your sweetheart?

22:46.510 --> 22:47.830
It might be Xiao Wuyi?

22:50.640 --> 22:52.550
Or it might be the Empress Dowager.

22:52.550 --> 22:54.210
But if Xiao Wuyi really did it,

22:54.830 --> 22:57.240
don't you hate him?

22:57.790 --> 22:58.650
In that battle,

22:59.200 --> 23:00.730
Xiao Wuyi won beautifully.

23:01.550 --> 23:02.310
He completely recaptured

23:02.310 --> 23:04.310
the Yushan Pass, which was lost
for nearly 20 years,

23:04.310 --> 23:05.910
and is my family's hometown.

23:06.960 --> 23:10.090
Tens of thousands of people returned
to their homeland.

23:10.930 --> 23:13.890
You tell me,
how am I supposed to hate him?

23:14.440 --> 23:16.160
Since then, I told myself

23:16.480 --> 23:17.710
to stop investigating.

23:17.710 --> 23:19.440
Even if it really was Xiao Wuyi,

23:20.750 --> 23:22.920
I would still be Heir's Consort.

23:24.880 --> 23:26.120
But that's all.

23:26.680 --> 23:27.740
The Heir only cares

23:27.790 --> 23:29.510
about his own goals.

23:31.160 --> 23:32.820
He doesn't care about anyone.

23:33.200 --> 23:34.030
Yes.

23:35.160 --> 23:38.020
So he will definitely
make the peace talks succeed,

23:38.400 --> 23:39.860
no matter what the cost is.

23:49.790 --> 23:52.030
Lady Xie won't be staying
in the manor for much longer.

23:52.030 --> 23:53.070
Once the peace talks are over,

23:53.070 --> 23:54.730
she will leave with Prince Qi.

23:54.830 --> 23:57.270
Your Highness's efforts are all in vain.

23:58.110 --> 24:00.170
Who told you I made them for Xie Jiayu?

24:01.510 --> 24:03.550
Your Highness,
is your appetite poor lately?

24:03.550 --> 24:05.750
Why do you love eating hawthorn so much?

24:06.160 --> 24:07.420
They are for Prince Qi.

24:07.960 --> 24:09.000
He wants to eat

24:09.000 --> 24:10.550
the hawthorn cake made by Lady Xie.

24:10.550 --> 24:12.080
Yet you let me do it instead.

24:14.310 --> 24:15.440
Where is my brother?

24:16.200 --> 24:17.550
Did he go to the racecourse
to find me again?

24:17.550 --> 24:20.030
Yes, he went to the racecourse
to find you again.

24:20.030 --> 24:21.490
He still wants to compete.

24:21.750 --> 24:23.110
You can't just keep dodging—

24:23.110 --> 24:24.510
it won't solve anything.

24:25.790 --> 24:27.510
Your Highness, the racecourse reported

24:27.510 --> 24:31.040
that Lady Xie secretly replaced
all the stirrups in the stable.

24:32.000 --> 24:33.330
The stirrup is so loose.

24:33.350 --> 24:35.350
Anyone riding it will fall off soon.

24:35.790 --> 24:36.960
If His Highness gets injured,

24:36.960 --> 24:37.830
he won't be able to compete.

24:37.830 --> 24:38.590
Could it be

24:39.440 --> 24:41.350
that Lady Xie was really persuaded
by the Grand Tutor,

24:41.350 --> 24:43.680
and is making a move against His Highness?

24:47.040 --> 24:47.680
Anmin.

24:49.350 --> 24:49.960
Don't.

25:00.830 --> 25:02.550
Young Master Yao,
there's something wrong with the stirrups.

25:02.550 --> 25:03.370
They were replaced.

25:03.370 --> 25:04.430
You can't use them.

25:04.720 --> 25:06.120
I replaced the stirrups.

25:06.790 --> 25:08.070
Yao's left leg is seriously injured.

25:08.070 --> 25:10.110
A standard stirrup does not
suit his archery on horseback.

25:10.110 --> 25:12.000
So I specially replaced them
with more stable ones.

25:12.000 --> 25:13.720
Then, after he goes to the battlefield,

25:13.720 --> 25:16.180
he will be no different
from a normal person.

25:16.640 --> 25:17.720
If you don't believe it,

25:17.720 --> 25:18.920
let him try it.

25:20.200 --> 25:21.600
I asked Lady Xie for help.

25:22.550 --> 25:24.750
Anmin, no.

25:26.440 --> 25:28.000
Are the stirrups not good enough,

25:28.000 --> 25:29.860
or am I, Xiao Yao, not good enough?

25:32.060 --> 25:33.920
This is the warhorse
that will accompany me in archery.

25:33.920 --> 25:34.880
Because of this,

25:35.480 --> 25:36.510
I have to try it.

25:37.310 --> 25:40.510
Over the years,
I've never given up on horseback archery.

25:40.510 --> 25:43.480
Nor have I forgotten
that I am a soldier of the Beifu Army.

25:43.480 --> 25:44.680
I never abandoned myself to despair.

25:44.680 --> 25:46.540
If it's just upper body strength,

25:46.590 --> 25:47.650
I am second to none.

25:48.680 --> 25:50.410
If it's really as Lady Xie said,

25:51.480 --> 25:53.640
I will compete in this match.

25:54.020 --> 25:54.550
It's no use hiding from me.

25:54.550 --> 25:55.350
Impossible.

26:01.480 --> 26:03.350
Xiao Wuyi, make a move.

26:03.720 --> 26:05.320
I don't need you to hold back.

26:05.350 --> 26:06.590
Test me yourself and see

26:06.590 --> 26:07.790
if I'm fit to compete.

26:12.270 --> 26:13.270
Now you won't even

26:13.270 --> 26:14.510
fight me?

26:15.200 --> 26:15.880
Anmin.

26:17.830 --> 26:19.430
Why won't you let me compete?

26:19.550 --> 26:20.590
I don't accept this!

26:20.590 --> 26:22.920
This concerns
the three northern prefectures.

26:22.920 --> 26:24.120
I can't take the risk.

26:24.550 --> 26:25.550
Say what you will,

26:26.200 --> 26:27.640
you still don't trust me.

26:27.920 --> 26:28.640
Xiao Wuyi,

26:28.830 --> 26:30.760
-I told you my horse can help.
-You—

26:30.780 --> 26:31.780
I trust even less.

26:32.310 --> 26:32.960
Xie Jiayu.

26:33.640 --> 26:35.750
I know you met Grand Tutor Xie
in the clinic.

26:35.750 --> 26:37.180
And I know what he talked to you about

26:37.180 --> 26:38.240
and what deal he made with you.

26:38.240 --> 26:39.350
You had me spied on?

26:40.470 --> 26:43.730
Burn all the stirrups and saddles
that Xie Jiayu replaced.

26:45.920 --> 26:47.230
Escort Anmin back to the manor.

26:47.230 --> 26:47.680
Yes.

26:48.960 --> 26:50.270
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

26:52.030 --> 26:52.750
Xiao Wuyi!

26:52.960 --> 26:54.200
Let go of me!

26:55.830 --> 26:57.270
Xiao Wuyi, let go of me!

26:57.550 --> 26:58.590
Let me go!

26:59.240 --> 27:00.030
Put me down!

27:00.030 --> 27:00.640
My Lady!

27:02.830 --> 27:04.030
-Xiao Wuyi.
-My Lady!

27:06.510 --> 27:07.240
Xiao Wuyi!

27:10.270 --> 27:10.830
My Lady!

27:12.660 --> 27:13.180
Get out.

27:23.190 --> 27:23.880
Save it.

27:24.720 --> 27:25.450
Stop acting.

27:31.660 --> 27:32.520
Then Xiao Wuyi,

27:33.030 --> 27:35.830
who are you trying to make
an example of by using me?

27:36.070 --> 27:37.600
You needn't put it that way.

27:43.400 --> 27:44.830
You have been in the army
for so many years.

27:44.830 --> 27:45.480
Whether the stirrups I made

27:45.480 --> 27:47.070
are harmful or helpful—

27:47.090 --> 27:48.640
you should know it very well.

27:48.640 --> 27:49.680
Even if you don't know,

27:49.680 --> 27:51.480
you would know if you let Yao try.

27:51.870 --> 27:53.440
But you were in such a hurry
to let Yan Yue burn them.

27:53.440 --> 27:54.310
Actually, you just

27:54.310 --> 27:55.770
don't want him to compete.

27:57.350 --> 27:59.160
Since you sent someone to watch me,

27:59.160 --> 28:00.720
you know very well

28:00.740 --> 28:01.720
whether I promised my father

28:01.720 --> 28:02.960
to sabotage your competition.

28:02.960 --> 28:04.550
Why did you put such a big blame on me?

28:04.550 --> 28:06.680
Why didn't you agree with your father?

28:07.350 --> 28:08.950
His words seemed like a deal,

28:09.640 --> 28:11.170
but were actually a threat.

28:11.310 --> 28:12.880
If you don't do as he asks,

28:13.350 --> 28:14.960
Li Lejun might really be pushed
into a political marriage

28:14.960 --> 28:15.830
by the noble families.

28:15.830 --> 28:17.350
And Yizhi won't be able to leave.

28:17.350 --> 28:18.410
Aren't you afraid?

28:18.640 --> 28:20.750
There are other ways
to stop the political marriage.

28:20.750 --> 28:23.240
But I will not trade three provinces
and their people for it,

28:23.240 --> 28:25.680
nor will I sacrifice the honor
of the Beifu soldiers.

28:25.680 --> 28:27.920
Xiao Wuyi, don't look down on me.

28:42.480 --> 28:43.680
As for you, Xiao Wuyi,

28:43.680 --> 28:44.240
you just

28:44.240 --> 28:45.920
don't want Yao to compete, right?

28:45.920 --> 28:47.480
You are afraid his military merits
will surpass yours

28:47.480 --> 28:48.810
and steal your thunder.

28:49.550 --> 28:50.830
I heard your horseback archery

28:50.830 --> 28:51.890
were taught by him.

28:53.550 --> 28:55.150
Xie Jiayu, don't provoke me.

28:56.440 --> 28:57.880
If you really want
to leave Jingan Mansion

28:57.880 --> 28:58.960
in one piece

28:59.160 --> 29:00.980
and live the carefree life
you and Yizhi dream of,

29:00.980 --> 29:02.240
mind your own business

29:02.240 --> 29:03.400
and stay away from me.

29:03.400 --> 29:05.130
Otherwise, I'm not sure if I...

29:14.030 --> 29:15.550
I can let you leave alive.

29:17.030 --> 29:18.200
You should be glad

29:19.480 --> 29:21.680
that I don't want to lose my best friend.

29:23.030 --> 29:23.680
Scared?

29:25.350 --> 29:26.270
You should be.

29:40.440 --> 29:41.000
My Lady.

29:42.440 --> 29:43.000
My Lady.

29:43.750 --> 29:44.510
Are you okay?

29:44.550 --> 29:46.080
Did His Highness bully you?

29:47.880 --> 29:49.640
It was just helping Yao out.

29:50.230 --> 29:51.760
Why was he acting like that?

29:54.720 --> 29:55.880
Before the competition,

29:55.880 --> 29:58.030
Xie Jiayu is not allowed to set
a single foot out of Wensheng Courtyard.

29:58.030 --> 29:58.630
Xiao Wuyi.

30:05.910 --> 30:06.550
Anmin?

30:07.510 --> 30:08.840
Did you ground Xie Jiayu

30:09.200 --> 30:11.680
because she helped me
improve the stirrups and saddles?

30:11.680 --> 30:12.740
You worry too much.

30:13.160 --> 30:14.750
Xie Jiayu is from a noble family.

30:14.750 --> 30:16.160
I was afraid she would ruin
the competition

30:16.160 --> 30:17.110
and ruin the Beifu Army's reputation.

30:17.110 --> 30:17.920
Nonsense.

30:18.640 --> 30:19.920
When I suspected her,

30:20.240 --> 30:21.240
you believed her.

30:21.380 --> 30:23.110
Now I am willing to believe her.

30:23.880 --> 30:26.110
Yet you're suspecting her
because she's from a noble family?

30:26.110 --> 30:27.670
You simply want
to use Xie Jiayu as an example

30:27.670 --> 30:28.880
to show everyone

30:29.010 --> 30:30.870
that absolutely no one is allowed

30:31.590 --> 30:33.790
to help me get a spot
in the competition.

30:33.840 --> 30:36.200
You have prepared
for the Beifu Army's reform for so long,

30:36.200 --> 30:38.160
but you never told me a word about it.

30:38.160 --> 30:39.000
In your eyes,

30:40.110 --> 30:41.240
am I just a piece of trash

30:41.240 --> 30:43.100
that the Beifu Army doesn't want?

31:18.350 --> 31:19.410
Lock this place up.

31:20.720 --> 31:22.050
I'm going out for a walk.

31:22.550 --> 31:23.480
Don't follow me.

31:31.880 --> 31:37.030
♪ The past is dust,
we're passing through ♪

31:37.950 --> 31:43.530
♪ No regrets for what we've lost and won ♪

31:39.640 --> 31:41.240
Why won't you let me compete?

31:41.440 --> 31:42.570
I don't accept this!

31:44.190 --> 31:50.490
♪ The shape of time begins to fade ♪

31:45.400 --> 31:46.270
In your eyes,

31:46.790 --> 31:48.000
am I just a piece of trash

31:48.000 --> 31:49.860
that the Beifu Army doesn't want?

31:50.760 --> 31:57.240
♪ Half by choice, half washed away ♪

31:57.760 --> 32:03.180
♪ If fate is fragile,
what is right or wrong ♪

32:02.000 --> 32:03.160
Anmin!

32:03.680 --> 32:04.510
Anmin!

32:03.780 --> 32:09.150
♪ We only live for what we can't let go ♪

32:08.830 --> 32:09.480
Yao.

32:09.680 --> 32:11.290
It's fine.

32:09.940 --> 32:13.590
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

32:12.200 --> 32:13.310
Don't scare me.

32:13.630 --> 32:14.110
Anmin!

32:13.690 --> 32:16.150
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

32:16.270 --> 32:17.270
What are you doing here?

32:16.370 --> 32:22.400
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

32:19.590 --> 32:21.590
Are you here to see if my son is dead?

32:21.590 --> 32:22.160
Darling.

32:22.400 --> 32:22.960
Darling.

32:22.670 --> 32:26.220
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

32:23.200 --> 32:24.350
You Lis

32:24.830 --> 32:26.880
took the life of one of my sons,

32:26.250 --> 32:29.220
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

32:27.550 --> 32:29.350
yet you're still living under his name.

32:29.240 --> 32:34.720
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

32:30.200 --> 32:33.110
Now, do you want the life
of my other son, too?

32:34.980 --> 32:38.720
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

32:38.740 --> 32:41.530
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

32:41.400 --> 32:42.200
Father.

32:41.550 --> 32:47.350
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

32:43.550 --> 32:44.510
Who am I?

32:47.790 --> 32:51.350
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

32:49.480 --> 32:52.070
When the Phoenix Heart Token appears,
peace shall be restored in the world.

32:51.620 --> 32:54.350
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

32:53.070 --> 32:53.930
Your Highness.

32:54.570 --> 33:01.120
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

32:54.960 --> 32:57.560
You are the son
of the late Emperor and Empress.

32:59.960 --> 33:01.510
You are the true heir of Ye.

33:02.030 --> 33:03.960
Now, the remaining Shadow Envoys

33:04.680 --> 33:05.920
are willing to follow you

33:05.920 --> 33:06.920
to restore order,

33:07.160 --> 33:08.290
reclaim the throne,

33:08.310 --> 33:09.590
trample Northern Qin,

33:10.440 --> 33:11.790
and return to the old capital!

33:11.790 --> 33:13.070
Trample Northern Qin!

33:13.310 --> 33:14.510
Return to the old capital!

33:13.840 --> 33:17.120
♪ Love and hate fade
like the shifting sand ♪

33:16.110 --> 33:16.880
Father.

33:17.140 --> 33:20.110
♪ What's right or wrong is better
left unsaid ♪

33:17.400 --> 33:18.640
I, Xiao Ju,

33:19.240 --> 33:20.510
am willing to follow you, Your Highness.

33:20.220 --> 33:25.870
♪ Every soul is bound by cause and fate ♪

33:26.290 --> 33:29.870
♪ The past is gone, so let it slip away ♪

33:29.950 --> 33:32.790
♪ The heart's a cage,
but peace will break the chains ♪

33:32.810 --> 33:38.860
♪ No need to speak,
just leave it all to fate ♪

33:53.720 --> 33:54.880
It's so late.

33:55.270 --> 33:56.880
Why isn't Wuyi back yet?

33:57.200 --> 33:57.960
Judging by the noise,

33:57.960 --> 33:59.890
he must still be at the racecourse.

34:00.000 --> 34:00.750
In Jiuzhang Plain,

34:00.750 --> 34:03.080
he suffered life-threatening injuries.

34:03.350 --> 34:05.880
He can't afford
to exhaust himself like this.

34:08.400 --> 34:09.360
Darling.

34:10.030 --> 34:12.090
How long are you going to punish Wuyi?

34:14.000 --> 34:15.150
I didn't punish him.

34:18.400 --> 34:20.440
But don't you think you two

34:20.710 --> 34:21.400
are too polite

34:21.400 --> 34:23.000
and distant with each other?

34:23.030 --> 34:25.130
You are closer to Yuanji, to Ruisheng,

34:25.130 --> 34:27.510
and even to that newlywed
from the Xie family

34:27.510 --> 34:29.150
than you are to Wuyi.

34:30.880 --> 34:32.480
When Wuyi came back injured,

34:32.510 --> 34:34.510
did you even ask about his injuries?

34:37.400 --> 34:38.190
I know.

34:39.150 --> 34:40.150
It's about Sheng.

34:41.630 --> 34:44.280
But Wuyi was just a baby then.

34:44.280 --> 34:46.409
If you want to blame someone, blame me.

34:47.880 --> 34:48.949
I don't blame him.

34:51.550 --> 34:54.550
Ever since he found out
who he really was,

34:55.920 --> 34:57.360
he has been fighting at the border

34:57.360 --> 34:58.760
and refused to come back.

34:59.990 --> 35:02.850
That's because he is afraid
you'll be sad to see him.

35:04.760 --> 35:05.510
And Anmin,

35:05.800 --> 35:07.030
he still doesn't know

35:07.740 --> 35:10.230
that it's you who doesn't want him
to return to the Northern Border

35:10.230 --> 35:11.890
and on the battlefield again.

35:13.550 --> 35:15.960
So he has taken all his resentment
over the years

35:15.960 --> 35:17.070
out on Wuyi.

35:18.230 --> 35:20.840
Fortunately, they are both tough
on the outside but warm on the inside.

35:20.840 --> 35:23.170
But if this misunderstanding continues,

35:24.060 --> 35:26.790
it will sooner or later turn
into real animosity.

35:36.030 --> 35:36.760
Darling,

35:39.400 --> 35:41.550
do you really want to see

35:41.550 --> 35:43.810
the two brothers at odds with each other?

35:59.550 --> 36:01.320
Anmin wants to return
to the Northern Border.

36:01.320 --> 36:02.050
That's good.

36:02.630 --> 36:04.630
Currently, the Beifu camps
are still short of organization.

36:04.630 --> 36:06.430
He has the talent to lead troops.

36:06.710 --> 36:08.170
If he is willing to return,

36:08.230 --> 36:11.690
your pressure on the western front
next year will be lessened.

36:12.590 --> 36:14.050
You are absolutely right.

36:16.180 --> 36:20.240
Quickly write to your mother and
tell Anmin to return to the battlefield.

36:27.760 --> 36:28.760
Young Master Yao.

36:29.150 --> 36:29.950
Don't help me.

36:34.680 --> 36:35.790
Stop practicing.

36:36.110 --> 36:38.370
Your leg can't take this kind of torment.

36:38.800 --> 36:40.510
Do you also think I'm useless?

36:41.000 --> 36:42.240
Even though I can't ride a horse,

36:42.240 --> 36:43.070
my archery

36:43.590 --> 36:44.920
and close combat skills

36:45.320 --> 36:46.980
are no worse than Xiao Wuyi's.

36:48.000 --> 36:50.070
He learned wrestling from me back then.

36:50.070 --> 36:52.230
On what grounds
does he stop me from competing?

36:52.230 --> 36:53.830
I'm worried about your legs.

36:54.590 --> 36:56.190
My father doesn't care about me.

36:56.190 --> 36:57.920
My younger brother looks down on me.

36:57.920 --> 36:58.840
Do you also...

37:08.000 --> 37:11.000
Prepare more medicine for bruises
and injuries for Young Master Yao.

37:11.000 --> 37:11.550
Yes.

37:52.280 --> 37:52.840
Nanxing.

37:53.630 --> 37:55.840
Don't you think this room is very stuffy?

37:55.840 --> 37:56.840
It's like a prison.

37:56.840 --> 37:57.960
It's only been two days,

37:57.960 --> 37:59.320
and you can't stay still anymore.

37:59.320 --> 38:00.710
Just like at home before,

38:00.710 --> 38:02.030
you always want to run outside.

38:02.030 --> 38:03.880
Her Highness couldn't control you.

38:03.880 --> 38:04.940
If this is a prison,

38:05.320 --> 38:07.780
it's the most wonderful prison
in the world.

38:09.710 --> 38:12.280
These are the recent requests
on Miraculous Craft.

38:12.280 --> 38:13.110
Take a look

38:13.110 --> 38:14.150
and see if there are
any mechanical gadgets

38:14.150 --> 38:15.550
that you're interested.

38:15.630 --> 38:17.440
You can make some to pass the time.

38:17.440 --> 38:18.590
The competition is in a few days.

38:18.590 --> 38:19.840
It will pass.

38:21.880 --> 38:23.280
A wooden kite
that can carry a person and fly.

38:23.280 --> 38:24.960
An arrow that bends its path
to pursue prey.

38:24.960 --> 38:26.880
Fire oil that cannot
be extinguished by water.

38:26.880 --> 38:28.110
And the buyers' names...

38:28.110 --> 38:29.130
Red Dragon, Black Dragon,

38:29.130 --> 38:30.530
Black Dragon, Full Moon.

38:31.230 --> 38:33.320
Isn't it obvious
they are Qing Long and Yan Yue?

38:33.320 --> 38:37.050
This must be Xiao Wuyi sending them
to make things difficult for me.

38:38.360 --> 38:40.070
So boring.

38:42.670 --> 38:43.960
Someone!

38:43.960 --> 38:44.960
Is anybody there?

38:56.320 --> 38:56.850
Let's go!

39:01.150 --> 39:02.760
The fire thunderstone of the Beifu Army

39:02.760 --> 39:04.360
is truly all bark and no bite.

39:04.590 --> 39:05.920
I don't know who designed them.

39:05.920 --> 39:07.320
They just wasted my time.

39:07.860 --> 39:08.860
I have to use mine.

39:20.710 --> 39:21.590
I'm a genius.

39:30.030 --> 39:30.630
Ghost!

39:31.000 --> 39:33.500
[Yuan Xiaole]

39:31.800 --> 39:33.930
Are you really Li Yunzhao's daughter?

39:35.440 --> 39:37.110
You don't look much like her.

39:37.550 --> 39:38.950
But you have some skills.

39:39.800 --> 39:41.630
I have to say,

39:41.800 --> 39:43.670
after you modified this fire thunderstone,

39:43.670 --> 39:45.270
its power actually increased quite a bit.

39:45.270 --> 39:47.000
How much saltpeter did you use?

39:47.000 --> 39:48.440
Hey, who are you?

39:48.510 --> 39:49.440
Do I know you?

39:49.680 --> 39:50.810
Move. I'm going out.

39:52.540 --> 39:53.340
Wait a minute.

39:54.590 --> 39:56.450
Xiao Wuyi really didn't lie to me.

39:56.760 --> 39:58.090
You do have some talent.

39:58.330 --> 39:59.320
I'm definitely taking you

39:59.320 --> 40:00.320
as my apprentice.

40:00.860 --> 40:03.050
Let me show you my fire thunderstone.

40:03.110 --> 40:04.840
Its power is no less than yours.

40:07.320 --> 40:09.380
Let's exchange our thoughts on this.

40:11.040 --> 40:12.510
Who said I'm going to be your apprentice?

40:12.510 --> 40:14.310
Are you drunk in broad daylight?

40:15.920 --> 40:18.180
Your temper is quite like your mother's.

40:18.440 --> 40:20.570
How could you possibly know my mother?

40:21.280 --> 40:22.920
Not only do I know her,

40:23.360 --> 40:25.420
but we fought a lot when we were young.

40:25.480 --> 40:26.810
Let me tell you a secret.

40:27.440 --> 40:29.700
Your mother doesn't have much time left.

40:31.550 --> 40:33.030
What did you say?

40:33.030 --> 40:33.760
Listen.

40:33.760 --> 40:35.310
Don't use seniority to boss me around.

40:35.310 --> 40:37.420
You designed this fire thunderstone?

40:37.420 --> 40:39.080
The design is truly terrible.

40:40.150 --> 40:41.810
What's wrong with it? Tell me.

40:42.280 --> 40:42.960
It's too big.

40:42.960 --> 40:45.420
Do you know
what "all bark and no bite" means?

40:46.000 --> 40:47.070
What do you know?

40:47.150 --> 40:47.800
Big?

40:48.510 --> 40:49.510
Its power is huge!

40:49.510 --> 40:52.110
The ones I design,
even if they are only this small,

40:52.110 --> 40:53.770
are more powerful than yours.

40:55.260 --> 40:55.920
Okay, okay.

40:56.550 --> 40:58.280
W-We'll talk about this later.

40:58.660 --> 40:59.520
Let me tell you.

40:59.960 --> 41:02.710
I've never been wrong in fortune-telling.

41:02.960 --> 41:06.070
Not only did I figure out that your mother
doesn't have much time left,

41:06.070 --> 41:09.230
but I also figured out
you will marry twice,

41:10.160 --> 41:11.920
no, three times in your life.

41:12.720 --> 41:14.800
And your husband, he'll die young.

41:16.230 --> 41:16.880
Is that so?

41:18.670 --> 41:19.880
Nanxing, get him!

41:21.190 --> 41:23.000
Who are you saying
doesn't have much time left?

41:23.000 --> 41:26.260
-Watch out for the fire thunderstone
-Who are you cursing?

41:37.440 --> 41:38.630
Why are you glaring at me?

41:38.630 --> 41:39.760
I told you to watch out
for the fire thunderstone.

41:39.760 --> 41:41.820
Watch out for the fire thunderstone.

41:44.030 --> 41:45.560
Qing Long, long time no see.

41:45.880 --> 41:46.740
Did you miss me?

41:53.310 --> 41:54.430
Give it back to me.

41:55.710 --> 41:57.630
You know how to make stirrups, too?

41:57.630 --> 41:58.280
At first glance,

41:58.280 --> 42:00.480
I knew this was designed for Xiao Yao.

42:01.070 --> 42:01.920
Xiao Wuyi

42:01.920 --> 42:03.670
asked me to design one before, too.

42:03.670 --> 42:04.620
My design

42:06.070 --> 42:07.530
was much better than this.

42:09.480 --> 42:10.840
You designed one for him, too?

42:10.840 --> 42:11.630
When?

42:12.760 --> 42:13.760
A long time ago.

42:16.360 --> 42:19.150
It was probably right
after Xiao Yao got injured.

42:20.360 --> 42:22.000
Xiao Wuyi was worried his brother

42:22.000 --> 42:23.930
couldn't get over his disability.

42:25.150 --> 42:25.880
It was a pity.

42:26.760 --> 42:28.970
He told me to stop
when the blueprint was only half done.

42:28.970 --> 42:29.820
Why stop?

42:30.670 --> 42:32.070
Naturally, it's because someone

42:32.070 --> 42:35.600
didn't want Xiao Yao to ride a horse
onto the battlefield again.

42:38.190 --> 42:38.840
Kiddo.

42:39.480 --> 42:41.710
You are quite talented

42:41.710 --> 42:42.630
in alchemy and metalworking,

42:42.630 --> 42:45.440
but your structural design
still lacks a bit.

42:47.410 --> 42:48.400
It's my blueprint. You...

42:48.400 --> 42:49.280
Hold on.

42:52.510 --> 42:53.000
Look.

42:54.840 --> 42:56.440
If it's connected like this,

42:56.630 --> 42:58.100
and then attached to the saddle,

42:58.100 --> 42:59.820
wouldn't it be much more flexible?

42:59.820 --> 43:00.850
The biggest problem with your design

43:00.850 --> 43:02.710
is that it's not flexible enough.

43:03.030 --> 43:04.150
It works fine with light pressure,

43:04.150 --> 43:06.360
but once too much force is applied,
it creates drag

43:06.360 --> 43:08.150
and can throw the rider off,

43:08.150 --> 43:09.840
leaving them vulnerable
to being trampled by their own horse.

43:09.840 --> 43:10.840
Wait, wait, wait.

43:11.070 --> 43:13.480
Did you say applying force
causes dragging?

43:13.480 --> 43:14.030
Oh, no.

43:14.320 --> 43:16.060
His Highness is testing the stirrups
for Young Master Yao.

43:16.060 --> 43:16.710
What?

43:56.110 --> 43:57.590
Why is it blurry again?
